OL,3,CEx-pro boxer tried to overturn police
OL,4,Cvan during riot
OL,6,FA former professional boxer who tried
OL,7,Fto overturn a police van during
OL,8,Frioting in Rotherham has been jailed.
OL,10,FLuke Crowcroft, 30, acted completely
OL,11,F"out of character" when he joined in
OL,12,Fmob violence outside a hotel housing
OL,13,Fasylum seekers, Sheffield Crown Court
OL,14,Fheard.
OL,16,FTrouble broke out after hundreds of
OL,17,Fpeople gathered for an anti-
OL,18,Fimmigration protest at the Holiday Inn
OL,19,FExpress, in Manvers, on 4 August.
