OL,3,CEx-pro boxer tried to overturn police
OL,4,Cvan during riot
OL,6,FPolice officers were attacked and the
OL,7,Fhotel's windows were smashed, forcing
OL,8,Fstaff to barricade themselves inside.
OL,9,FA bin was pushed against the building
OL,10,Fand set alight.
OL,12,FDoncaster-based Crowcroft was part of
OL,13,Fa group which rocked a police van,
OL,14,Fleaving those inside terrified, the
OL,15,Fcourt heard.
OL,17,FEd Moss, mitigating, told the court
OL,18,Fhow Crowcroft was a successful boxer
OL,19,Ffrom an early age, represented his
OL,20,Fcountry as an amateur and later became
OL,21,Fthe youngest professional.
