OL,3,CEx-pro boxer tried to overturn police
OL,4,Cvan during riot
OL,6,FHe told the court: "This is a man who,
OL,7,Fall of his life, has been disciplined."
OL,9,FMr Moss said: "It is simply not in his
OL,10,Fnature. It is just bizarre to everyone
OL,11,Fwho knows him why he was there and
OL,12,Fdoing what he did.
OL,14,F"Out of character simply doesn't do it
OL,15,Fjustice".
OL,17,FMr Moss said Crowcroft was devoted to
OL,18,Fthe 15-year-old son of his partner,
OL,19,Fwho has a number of problems, and the
OL,20,Fdefendant is a key part of his care.
