OL,6,FHe said: "He wishes me, on his behalf,
OL,7,Fto apologise to everybody ` to the
OL,8,Fcourt, to the police, to his own
OL,9,Ffamily."
OL,11,FJudge Sarah Wright was shown video
OL,12,Ffootage of how the police dog van was
OL,13,Fviolently rocked by a group outside
OL,14,Fthe hotel.
OL,16,FThe court was told how there was a
OL,17,Fchief inspector and a PC inside, as
OL,18,Fwell as a dog, and a statement from
OL,19,Fthe junior officer outlined how he was
OL,20,Fterrified the vehicle was going to be
OL,21,Foverturned and set on fire.
