OL,4,Cvan during riot
OL,6,FCrowcroft, of Danesway, Scawthorpe,
OL,7,FDoncaster, admitted violent disorder
OL,8,Fat a previous hearing. He was jailed
OL,9,Ffor two-and-a-half years.
OL,11,FJudge Wright also jailed 19-year-old
OL,12,FAshley Lowe on Monday after she heard
OL,13,Fhow he took part in various aspects of
OL,14,Fthe disorder, including entering the
OL,15,Fhotel building after a fire door had
OL,16,Fbeen smashed-in.
