OL,6,FThe court heard how Lowe, who was 18
OL,7,Fat the time, was first caught on
OL,8,Fcamera pulling down fencing which was
OL,9,Fthen used by the mob to throw at
OL,10,Fpolice and fuel the fire in a bin
OL,11,Foutside the fire door.
OL,13,FHe was then seen going into the hotel
OL,14,Ffor a short period before confronting
OL,15,Fofficers outside as they came under a
OL,16,Fbarrage of missiles.
OL,18,FIn one piece of footage Lowe, of North
OL,19,FStreet, Darfield, is heard shouting
OL,20,F"Oi! Charge!".
