OL,6,FRoofer Ben Beardsley, 38, of Hall
OL,7,FGate, Mexborough, was jailed for two
OL,8,Fyears and eights months after Judge
OL,9,FWright watched footage of him in the
OL,10,Fcrowd wearing a Guy Fawkes mask and
OL,11,Fthrowing a missile at officers.
OL,13,FMr Baptiste, this time defending
OL,14,Ffather-of-two Beardsley, said: "He
OL,15,Fdoesn't have any political or racist
OL,16,Fviews whatsoever.
OL,18,F"He got caught up in what was going
OL,19,Fon. He was throwing items that were
OL,20,Fhanded to him."
